RStudio Connect at GRAIL

December BARUG Meetup

Emma Rudi

What is RStudio Connect?

A publishing platform / content hub for

  • Shiny applications
  • R Markdown reports
  • dashboards
  • plots
  • and more!

Wait, but why?

Now with Rstudio Connect:

Wins:

  • R-users of all levels enjoy easy publishing
  • URLs are easily shareable and update-able
  • central location to browse analyses of other groups leads to unexpected insight and collaboration

Challenges:

  • publishing too soon to too many people
  • tags as opposed to folders
  • setting up authentication to work with our custom user-access to S3
